      <reaction compartment="compartment_7660" fast="false" id="reaction_1015702" metaid="metaid_93" name="Expression of IFN-induced genes" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Around 300 IFN-induced genes have been identified from different oligonucleotide microarray studies in melanoma (WM9) and fibrosarcoma (HT1080) cell lines as well as from human dendritic cells treated with IFN. Only the proteins which are well studied and their function characterized are represented here.</p>
        </notes>
        <annotation>
          <rdf:RDF xmlns:rdf="http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:vCard="http://www.w3.org/2001/vcard-rdf/3.0#" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:bqbiol="http://biomodels.net/biology-qualifiers/">
