      <reaction compartment="compartment_70101" fast="false" id="reaction_909725" metaid="metaid_96" name="Interaction of IRF9 with p-STAT2:p-STAT1" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">The phosphorylated STAT2:STAT1 heterodimer associates with interferon-regulating factor 9 (IRF9) to form the interferon-stimulated gene factor 3 (ISGF3) complex.</p>
