      <reaction compartment="compartment_70101" fast="false" id="reaction_909722" metaid="metaid_117" name="Release of p-STAT2:p-STAT1 dimer" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">The phosphorylated STAT2:STAT1 heterodimers thus formed disassociate from the IFNAR1 subunit and translocates to the nucleus.</p>
        </notes>
